### 头像相关接口测试

### AI 优化头像
POST http://localhost:8000/avatar/optimize
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "image_url": "https://example.com/original-avatar.jpg"
}

# Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "code": 0,
#     "message": "ok",
#     "data": {
#         "image_url": "https://oss.example.com/resume-avatars/xxx/optimized.jpg"
#     }
# }

###

### 修改头像背景色
POST http://localhost:8000/avatar/change-background
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "image_url": "https://example.com/original-avatar.jpg",
    "background_color": "lightblue"
}

# Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "code": 0,
#     "message": "ok",
#     "data": {
#         "image_url": "https://oss.example.com/resume-avatars/xxx/bg-changed.jpg"
#     }
# }

###
